<h2 id="run-on-most-popular-linux-distributions">Run on most popular Linux distributions</h2>

<ul>
  <li>The <strong>SADMIN client</strong> have been tested to work on Redhat, Fedora, CentOS, Debian, Ubuntu, Raspbian and Aix.
    <ul>
      <li>It should work on most Linux distribution.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>The <strong>SADMIN server</strong>  is only supported Redhat, CentOS, Debian, Ubuntu and Raspbian.</li>
  <li>Install time is about 15 minutes.</li>
  <li>We have been working for more than two years on these tools and it‚Äôs near version 1.0.</li>
  <li>We will continue to add and enhance the SADMIN tools over the years to come.</li>
</ul>

<p><a href="#brief-description">Back To The Top</a></p>

