<h2 id="download">Download</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Download the latest version of the SADMIN Project from our <a href="https://www.sadmin.ca/www/download.php">Download page</a>.</li>
  <li>Have a look at our <a href="https://www.sadmin.ca/www/changelog.php">changelog</a> and see the latest features.</li>
  <li>You can also clone the project from <a href="https://github.com/jadupl2/sadmin">GitHub</a>
    <ul>
      <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">git clone https://github.com/jadupl2/sadmin.git</code></li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

