<h2 id="sadmin-support">SADMIN Support</h2>
<p>Should you ran into problem while installing or running the SADMIN tools, please run the ‚Äòsadm_support_request.sh‚Äô, attach the resulting file to an email with a description of your
problem or question and sent it to <a href="mailto:support@sadmin.ca">support@sadmin.ca</a>.
We will get back to you as soon as possible.</p>

